<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.7.7">
<l>uḷaṅkaṉin tirukku muṉṉaiyē pitaṟṟu muṉakkaṉṟi yeṉakkaṉpoṉ ṟilaḷāl</l>
<l>vaḷaṅkaṉi poḻilcūḻ māliruñ cōlai māyaṉē yeṉṟuvāy veruvum</l>
<l>kaḷaṅkaṉi muṟuval kārikai peritu kavalaiyō ṭavalañcērn tirunta</l>
<l>viḷaṅkaṉi yivaḷuk keṉṉiṉain tiruntā yiṭaventai yentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She chatters only of you for whom her heart is melting;</l>
<l rend="indent">she certainly has no love for me, [it] not being for you.</l>
<l>“Māyaṉ of Māliruñcōlai encircled by groves of plentiful fruit,” she babbles.</l>
<l>What were you intending, lord father of Iṭaventai, for [my] sweet young girl,</l>
<l>This beauty with currant berry lips who is [so] greatly acquainted</l>
<l rend="indent">with pain and distress?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
